  <entry>
    <title>Python中Faker库(生成虚假数据)</title>
    <link href="/2023/08/10/Python%E4%B8%ADFaker%E5%BA%93-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E8%99%9A%E5%81%87%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE/"/>
    <url>/2023/08/10/Python%E4%B8%ADFaker%E5%BA%93-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E8%99%9A%E5%81%87%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="基本用法"><a href="#基本用法" class="headerlink" title="基本用法"></a>基本用法</h2><h3 id="1-pip安装"><a href="#1-pip安装" class="headerlink" title="1.pip安装"></a>1.pip安装</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">pip install Faker<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-引用"><a href="#2-引用" class="headerlink" title="2.引用"></a>2.引用</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> faker <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> Faker<br>fake = Faker(locale=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;zh_CN&#x27;</span>) <span class="hljs-comment"># 默认英文，中文设置为&quot;zh_CN&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span> (fake.email())<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(fake.country())<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(fake.name())<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(fake.text())<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(fake.latitude(), fake.longitude())<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(fake.url())<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出成功(每次都不同)：</p><div class="note note-success">            <p><a href="mailto:&#110;&#119;&#97;&#110;&#x40;&#x65;&#120;&#97;&#x6d;&#112;&#108;&#x65;&#x2e;&#x6e;&#101;&#116;">&#110;&#119;&#97;&#110;&#x40;&#x65;&#120;&#97;&#x6d;&#112;&#108;&#x65;&#x2e;&#x6e;&#101;&#116;</a><br>所罗门群岛<br>李龙<br>点击看到需要有些其他品牌到了.今天的话经验非常活动中国以上.主要安全推荐中心男人谢谢系统.<br>标准经济一次一下.不能电话不断免费根据阅读.主题地方帮助工具只要说明.<br>下载标题文章她的只是联系公司.本站得到密码结果文件同时.查看等级问题全国工程实现.<br>不要不过音乐然后成为资源.朋友自己开发虽然是否组织帖子运行.拥有生产文章计划操作语言.<br>投资为什应该那么.<br>-4.851112 -105.639433</p>          </div><h3 id="3-小应用"><a href="#3-小应用" class="headerlink" title="3.小应用"></a>3.小应用</h3><h4 id="应用1"><a href="#应用1" class="headerlink" title="应用1"></a>应用1</h4><p><span class="label label-primary">创建一个包含100名学生的json，名为students.json，其中包含学生姓名、地址、位置坐标和学生学号。</span></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> faker <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> Faker<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># To create a json file</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> json<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># For student id</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> random <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> randint<br><br>fake = Faker(locale=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;zh_CN&quot;</span>)<br><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">input_data</span>(<span class="hljs-params">x</span>):<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># dictionary</span><br>    student_data = &#123;&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, x):<br>        student_data[i] = &#123;&#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 编号</span><br>        student_data[i][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;id&#x27;</span>] = randint(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">100</span>)<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 姓名</span><br>        student_data[i][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;name&#x27;</span>] = fake.name()<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 住址</span><br>        student_data[i][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;address&#x27;</span>] = fake.address()<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 纬度</span><br>        student_data[i][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;latitude&#x27;</span>] = <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>(fake.latitude())<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 经度</span><br>        student_data[i][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;longitude&#x27;</span>] = <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>(fake.longitude())<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(student_data)<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># dictionary dumped as json in a json file</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;students.json&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;w&#x27;</span>, encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;utf-8&#x27;</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> fp:<br>        json.dump(student_data, fp, ensure_ascii=<span class="hljs-literal">False</span>)  <span class="hljs-comment"># ensure_ascii=False 防止转为ASCII码值</span><br><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;__main__&#x27;</span>:<br>    input_data(<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>文件结果：</p><p><img src="/2023/08/10/Python%E4%B8%ADFaker%E5%BA%93-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E8%99%9A%E5%81%87%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE/image-20230810100057820.png" alt="students.json"></p><h4 id="应用2"><a href="#应用2" class="headerlink" title="应用2"></a>应用2</h4><p><span class="label label-primary">创建虚假个人资料</span></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> faker <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> Faker<br><br>fake = Faker(locale=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;zh_CN&quot;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(fake.profile())<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出结果：</p><div class="note note-success">            <p>{‘job’: ‘宠物护理&#x2F;美容’, ‘company’: ‘彩虹传媒有限公司’, ‘ssn’: ‘653100197810109931’, ‘residence’: ‘河北省小红市清城澳门路W座 804179’, ‘current_location’: (Decimal(‘77.879188’), Decimal(‘115.676105’)), ‘blood_group’: ‘O+’, ‘website’: [‘<a href="http://www.yaotian.cn/">http://www.yaotian.cn/</a>‘, ‘<a href="http://gu.cn/">http://gu.cn/</a>‘, ‘<a href="http://jing.cn/">http://jing.cn/</a>‘, ‘<a href="http://qp.org/']">http://qp.org/&#39;]</a>, ‘username’: ‘shijie’, ‘name’: ‘彭斌’, ‘sex’: ‘F’, ‘address’: ‘香港特别行政区玉英市静安合肥路Z座 362979’, ‘mail’: ‘<a href="mailto:&#113;&#105;&#x61;&#110;&#109;&#105;&#x6e;&#x67;&#x40;&#104;&#x6f;&#x74;&#x6d;&#x61;&#105;&#108;&#x2e;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;">&#113;&#105;&#x61;&#110;&#109;&#105;&#x6e;&#x67;&#x40;&#104;&#x6f;&#x74;&#x6d;&#x61;&#105;&#108;&#x2e;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;</a>‘, ‘birthdate’: datetime.date(2014, 12, 10)}</p>          </div><hr><p>未完待续</p><h2 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h2><section class="footnotes"><div class="footnote-list"><ol><li><span id="fn:1" class="footnote-text"><span><a href="https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/secrets-python-module-generate-secure-random-numbers/?ref=ml_lbp">Secrets | Python module to Generate secure random numbers - GeeksforGeeks</a><a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref"> ↩</a></span></span></li></ol></div></section>]]></content>
    
    
